item.title: Ricki Lake Files For Divorce From Husband Christian Evans
item.description: It's over! Ricki Lake has filed for divorce from her husband of two and a half years Christian Evans, TMZ reports.   According to the site, Lake, who cited irreconcilable differences, filed the papers on Oct. 16, just one week after the couple separated on Oct. 9. Lake's filing appears to be gracious — TMZ reports the host is offering to pay Evans, a jewelry designer, spousal support. Thank You! You have successfully subscribed.

item.title: Rootsuit Shark Tank Founder, Net Worth, and Investment
item.description: RootSuit, the skin-tight full-body neon suit, made its debut on season 4 of Shark Tank USA in 2013. The founder, Colin Grussing, pitched the unique swimwear product to the sharks in the hopes of securing a $100,000 investment for a 15% equity stake in the company. However, the sharks expressed confusion about the functionality of RootSuit and how it differed from other swimsuits on the market. As a result, they declined to invest, leaving Colin Grussing without a deal.

item.title: Why Kate Winslet Thought Shed Get Fired From The Holiday
item.description: Although new holiday movies are released every year, there are some festive films that fans will never tire of watching. The Holiday, starring Kate Winslet, Cameron Diaz, Jack Black, and Jude Law, is one such film that tends to appear again and again in Christmas movie marathons around the world. And even though newer Christmas films have been named The Holiday knock offs, like the upcoming Ashton Kutcher and Reese Witherspoon flick Your Place or Mine, there can only ever be one The Holiday.

item.description: Highlights Kaley Cuoco and Karl Cook's marriage ended after just three years. The couple had a unique living arrangement, living separately for the majority of their marriage. item.title: Luh Tyler Height: How the Teenage Rapper Stands Out in the Hip Hop Scene
item.description: Luh Tyler is a rising star in the hip hop industry, who has gained fame and recognition for his viral songs and his impressive talent.
